06cfd1887509c9ccfe26634bcf426611f1b7d79ff2e7d12795915fdbfefc031a73788f2b4359072e7869afb2938ae94adc648768d74b976376962f98ddadbdf1  0001-Add-provisioner-for-Alpine-Linux.patch
"
